{
  "stem": "18575.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to make-- I-- so I remember I made-- the first one that I made was a coat-hanging bar for hats and coats that you hang from with.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I can tell you that the first or second year in class they did not have yet in the school-- it was a new school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't have the classes for manual labor, [? or-- ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they taught us-- it was, by the way, the public school was coeducational in the first grades-- taught us how to knit and how to sew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know how to knit, and I know how to repair socks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what they call that method, whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had one-- one a year, once [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to sit with the girls, so we had to learn that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because while the boys were working woodwork, the girls would work on it-- girls' work, so to say-- sewing, knitting, crocheting, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was basically-- We also had in the fifth grade, I think, we had the first year of French-- of French that we took.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took Latin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was in the Soviet Union in school, I took Latin--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--as a class, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was we had the gym, and it was once a week, compulsory gym, which were the gym stepladders and horses and all the things that we had to attend.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did none.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing except what I mentioned before-- what my father has planned for me, not necessarily what I would wind up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was the talk in the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first of all, of course, we played soccer in the streets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Soccer is the popular game.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
